<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>RADSerial</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">`RADSerial`<sp/>provides<sp/>Linux<sp/>serial<sp/>port<sp/>support<sp/>through<sp/>`RADSerial::RADSerialPort`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">It<sp/>uses<sp/>`RADCore::RADIODevice`<sp/>and<sp/>posts<sp/>read<sp/>availability<sp/>through<sp/>`RADCore::EventLoop`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Core<sp/>features:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>Baud<sp/>rate,<sp/>data<sp/>bits,<sp/>parity,<sp/>stop<sp/>bits,<sp/>and<sp/>flow<sp/>control<sp/>configuration.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>Async<sp/>`readyRead`<sp/>delivery.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>`RADIODevice`<sp/>read/write<sp/>compatibility.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>Basic<sp/>`/dev`<sp/>serial<sp/>port<sp/>discovery.</highlight></codeline>
